				\begin{document}$${{\mbox{L}}}p\,{{\mbox{(m)=}}}\sqrt{{\tau }_{p}\times {{{{{{\rm{D}}}}}}}_{p}}$$\end{document}Where τp is the minority carrier lifetime of n-type Si, which is above 11 µs in our study, and Dp (12.4 cm2/s at 298 K) is the diffusion coefficient of the hole.

